name: BG65 Titanium
description:
BG65 Titanium features a compound titanium hydride coating that provides a sharp yet comfortable feel at impact. Designed for hard hitters.

Gauge: 0.70 mm
Length: 10 m (33 ft) / 200 m (656 ft)
Core: High Polymer Nylon Multifilament
Outer: Special Braided High Polymer Nylon Fiber
Coating: Compound Titanium Hydride
Made in Japan
